504
00:28:16,939 --> 00:28:17,739
Itago mo.

505
00:28:18,060 --> 00:28:18,939
Magkunwari kang hindi nangyari.

506
00:28:20,820 --> 00:28:21,820
Sige, Binibini.

507
00:28:24,820 --> 00:28:26,419
Mas magaling si Sili Hutong.

508
00:28:26,820 --> 00:28:28,419
Maaaring matigas ang panganay na binibini,

509
