573
00:30:49,340 --> 00:30:51,060
Hindi ako makatulog buong gabi.

574
00:30:51,739 --> 00:30:52,620
At ngayon,

575
00:30:52,620 --> 00:30:53,860
Nakilala kita pagkalabas ko pa lang.

576
