Magpakita ka naman ng respeto.

600
00:31:33,140 --> 00:31:33,820
Sino ka, girl?
Gumalaw ka.

601
00:31:34,780 --> 00:31:35,620
Tara na.

602
00:31:36,419 --> 00:31:37,259
