615
00:31:58,939 --> 00:32:01,300
Huwag mong sabihing si Yao Wenxiu 'yan.

616
00:32:02,540 --> 00:32:03,659
Nababaliw ka na ba?

617
00:32:06,340 --> 00:32:07,699
Bakit ka laging nandyan?

618
00:32:09,939 --> 00:32:11,259
Miss, sige lang.

619
00:32:11,620 --> 00:32:12,259
Ako na ang bahala dito.

620
00:32:13,459 --> 00:32:14,300
Dali! Masakit 'yan!

621
00:32:15,659 --> 00:32:16,699
Tumabi.

622
00:32:21,140 --> 00:32:21,900
Gu Jinzhao!

623
00:32:22,580 --> 00:32:23,659
Magbabayad ka para dito!

624
00:32:26,100 --> 00:32:27,100
Dakilang Tutor Xue

625
00:32:27,100 --> 00:32:28,540
