650
00:33:21,300 --> 00:33:22,179
Salamat po, Ginang.

651
00:33:23,300 --> 00:33:24,499
Noong una, akala ko lang

652
00:33:24,499 --> 00:33:26,060
Qinglan, sa parehong pamilya

653
00:33:26,380 --> 00:33:27,419
