688
00:35:02,900 --> 00:35:04,419
Gusto mo bang sumali sa negosyo ko?

689
00:35:10,820 --> 00:35:12,059
Ito ang pera

690
00:35:12,059 --> 00:35:13,260
Nakaipon ako sa mga nakalipas na taon.

691
00:35:14,260 --> 00:35:15,180
Binilang ko ito.

692
00:35:15,499 --> 00:35:16,820
Ito ay 8,000 tael sa kabuuan.

693
00:35:17,939 --> 00:35:18,780
Maaari mong makuha ang lahat.

694
00:35:20,459 --> 00:35:21,539
8,000 taels

695
00:35:21,740 --> 00:35:22,700
