696
00:35:23,180 --> 00:35:23,820
Hindi sapat.

697
00:35:24,579 --> 00:35:26,099
Nang ikasal ang Pangalawang Kapatid kay Yao Wenxiu,

698
00:35:26,340 --> 00:35:28,139
Ang kanyang dote na pilak pa lamang ay 20,000 tael na.

699
00:35:28,979 --> 00:35:30,499
Kahit papaano ay mamaya

700
00:35:30,619 --> 00:35:31,660
