705
00:35:39,820 --> 00:35:42,539
Gusto mo bang kumita ng sarili mong dote?

706
00:35:44,700 --> 00:35:45,340
Oo.

707
00:35:46,660 --> 00:35:48,499
Nagdurusa pa rin ang nanay ko sa templo.

708
00:35:48,900 --> 00:35:50,459
At ganoon pa rin si tatay.

709
00:35:51,740 --> 00:35:53,419
Kailangan kong hanapin ang sarili kong paraan.

710
00:35:54,419 --> 00:35:55,700
Matutulungan mo ba ako?

711
00:35:55,860 --> 00:35:56,860
Hayaan mong makibahagi ako
sa negosyo mo.

712
00:35:58,459 --> 00:35:59,539
Wala akong pakialam kung anong hanapbuhay iyon.

713
00:35:59,740 --> 00:36:00,419
Hindi rin ako sakim.

714
00:36:00,700 --> 00:36:01,860
Basta't kumikita ito.

715
00:36:05,419 --> 00:36:06,059
Hindi.

716
00:36:12,019 --> 00:36:13,220
Hindi pa ba sapat ang pera?

717
00:36:13,939 --> 00:36:14,780
Magkakamot pa ako.

718
00:36:16,260 --> 00:36:17,419
Hindi ito tungkol sa pera.

719
00:36:18,059 --> 00:36:19,260
Kahit gaano kalaki ang iaalok mo,

720
00:36:19,459 --> 00:36:20,619
Hindi ako sasagot ng oo.

721
00:36:21,539 --> 00:36:22,300
Bumalik ka.

722
00:36:24,380 --> 00:36:25,220
Bakit?

723
00:36:29,340 --> 00:36:30,099
Jinzhao.

724
00:36:30,860 --> 00:36:32,260
Alam kong ayaw mo sa akin.

725
00:36:32,860 --> 00:36:33,900
Ngunit

726
00:36:34,099 --> 00:36:35,619
magkapatid pa rin tayo.

727
00:36:36,700 --> 00:36:37,740
Tulungan mo ako.

728
00:36:38,019 --> 00:36:39,099
Hayaan mong makibahagi ako

729
00:36:39,099 --> 00:36:40,019
sa iyong negosyo.

730
00:36:41,220 --> 00:36:42,300
Paano kung mawalan ito ng pera?

731
00:36:44,539 --> 00:36:45,499
Negosyo

732
00:36:45,900 --> 00:36:47,499
maaari ring mawalan ng pera.

733
00:36:48,180 --> 00:36:49,300
Sabi mo lang

734
00:36:49,300 --> 00:36:50,180
hindi ka naging sakim,

735
00:36:50,539 --> 00:36:51,780
na anumang tubo ay makakatulong.

736
00:36:52,780 --> 00:36:54,059
Ang pangungusap na iyon lamang

737
00:36:54,539 --> 00:36:55,419
