746
00:37:29,740 --> 00:37:30,740
Nandito na si Qing.

747
00:37:33,900 --> 00:37:36,459
Lola. Tiyo. Tita.

748
00:37:37,099 --> 00:37:38,740
Nakabalik ka na. Umupo ka.

